title: Watch Indian River's Win Over Fowler
text:
Watch Indian River's Win Over Fowler   12, 2015 at 5:20 AM   12, 2015 at 5:20 AM EDT 
If you missed Indian River's trouncing of Fowler Friday night, you're still in luck. The football game was webcast live on www.wwnytv.com , but still can be seen here . Enjoy the game.
